<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.82.0">Hugo</generator><title type="html">screenlock on Sebastian Hoß</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenlock/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenlock/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenlock/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2021-04-19T02:41:01+00:00</updated><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenlock/</id><entry><title type="html">Lock your screen on SwayWM</title><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/lock-your-screen-on-swaywm/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><link href="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/taken-screenshots-on-swaywm/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Taken screenshots on SwayWM"/><id>https://seb.people.metio.wtf/topic/lock-your-screen-on-swaywm/</id><published>2021-04-05T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2021-04-05T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://swaywm.org/">SwayWM</a> uses can use a mixture of <a href="https://github.com/swaywm/swaylock">swaylock</a> to lock their screen. Place the following key binding in your Sway config:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c1">#</span>
<span class="c1"># Screen lock</span>
<span class="c1">#</span>
bindsym <span class="nv">$mod</span>+Ctrl+l <span class="nb">exec</span> swaylock -c <span class="m">000000</span>
</code></pre></div><p><code>$mod+Ctrl+l</code> will lock your screen and turn it to black.</p>
]]></content><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/categories/snippet" term="snippet" label="snippet"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/swaywm" term="swaywm" label="swaywm"/><category scheme="https://seb.people.metio.wtf/tags/screenlock" term="screenlock" label="screenlock"/></entry></feed>